thread.title: es

author: es
title: es
text:
Good site and good range of items at good prices. Easy ordering and delivery. The only issue is difficulty finding a way to communicate if there are any problems.
Also I have only just ordered my items so I cannot comment on them yet, nor the delivery. So I will have to give 4 stars based on the site being decent and the range and price being decent.
I will make it 5 stars if the items are also good and are delivered without issues.
